                        <p>First, dial 911 or look for help somewhere else. As soon as you arrive, check to see whether the victim is still breathing and whether the area is secure. If it turns out to be essential, provide first assistance and take stock of the situation. In a crisis scenario, volatile and flammable components may be decisive in determining who lives and dies. <br><br>

